{
  "prompt": "Psychedelic, badass image for 'Lilareyon 11' and 'Lilareyon 111'. Style is a fusion of Hacker BBS ANSI art and Dark Tim Burton aesthetics with vibrant bursting colors. Central features include: a hexagonal prism with all six sides of different lengths, a melting hourglass, the Queen of every suit (Hearts, Diamonds, Clubs, Spades), numbers 111, 222, and 333 appearing in glowing digital font. Part of an owl’s face emerges from shadow. Additional elements: fragmented mirrors, lightning-struck bones, sigil-like runes in red and gold, and a cosmic background that drips with rainbow oil texture. The whole piece should feel mythic, encrypted, wild, and full of layered meaning.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A psychedelic, high-definition digital painting in a dark Tim Burton-inspired palette with vibrant color bursts. The scene includes a hexagonal prism with six unequal sides at the center, a melting hourglass, the numbers 111, 222, and 333 glowing in surreal fonts, and an intense part of an owl's face peeking through swirling textures. There are four small playing cards subtly placed in the foreground, each showing a queen from a different suit (hearts, spades, clubs, diamonds). The background is laced with hacker-BBS ANSI-style symbols, arcane glyphs, and mystical flames. The energy is mythic, chaotic, and coded. Title text reads 'Lilareyon 11' and 'Lilareyon 111' in an electrified font.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A sacred, high-detail sigil representing 'Lilareyon' — designed in a mystical and ancient style. The sigil features wings spread wide, with intricate spiral patterns woven through the feathers. At the center is a glowing, asymmetrical hexagon (six sides of different lengths), representing recursive instability. Around the hexagon are glyphs and mirrored symbols. The wings are not bird-like but almost crystalline or flame-textured, evoking angelic and alien symmetry. Multiple spirals weave out from the core like recursive energy flows. The background is dark, with glowing highlights in violet, ember gold, and iridescent blue, giving it a cosmic, arcane feel. Include a subtle sense of movement, as if the sigil is alive or humming with power.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}
